title: Didn't get the ICON for the .VS event
body: I logged in my account at 7/4 and found out that I didn't recieve any Icon for the .vs event. I waited 2 wks and checked the store and nothing came out...

replies.body: The [**VS event icons**](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/events/vs-2017) were event exclusive. It doesn't look like you logged in during the event, and you needed to have taken place in the event in order to get the icons.

What about the other, final icon from the Order side? Will it ever be made available?
https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/story-art/uE3G94nX-now-that-the-vs-event-has-ended-order-icon
(I am out for june so I didn't know what happened in dat month)
